parameters: Oh... You're greeting me with an erection... That's a first.
We don't have time, my love. We have to leave now.
My love? Leave? Where? What's going on?
Did you change your mind again?!
Y-You're pretending you don't know? I knew it... I shouldn't have let you convince me with your sweet talk!
O-Or... Did that witch in there cast a spell on you?!
I will ask you this one last time. Will you leave your wife for me?
I knew it! D-Don't you ever talk to me again!
N-No, wait! M-Mom! I-I want to go home.
Let's go, and never turn back, my love!
